rComments: This was a summer course. Alot of work for a summer course and he expected alot. Not an easy class and you should be sure to attend all lectures. His test have 50% lecture material and 50% textbook material. The material was often different but related to eachother.

AMAZING PROF! lectures (although 2 hours) were very interesting! his use of clear slides, interesting articles, video clips, and jokes actually encouraged me to come to class. essays were very straight forward. same with tests. material covered in class was exactly what was on the tests and exam. if you go to class you'll get an A =)
He is my new favourite prof! He makes lectures very entertaining and interesting. His tests are fair and you can truly tell he cares about his work, which is very refreshing. Highly recommended!
